skins.shipDescription: Leander-class light cruiser ¨C Leander, Hull Number 75!
skins.selfIntroduction: I am the Leander class light cruiser, Leander. Me and my sister Achilles had worked hard around different countries. Please tell me about the things that I need to improve on. I'll do my best.
skins.acquisition: Good day to you. I am Leander class' light cruiser, Leander. Actually, I have some differences from my sisters. Do you want to know what they are?
skins.login: Oh my, Commander. Please take care of me today as well.
skins.details: Mmm. I'll leave it to you then, Commander.
skins.secretaryIdle1: Commander, are you tired? Do you want to lay on my thighs?
skins.secretaryIdle2: The place I used to live in was very warm
skins.secretaryIdle3: Aiiiiiiiiieeei!!!... Oh my... it's you, Commander-- Geez, you surprised me...
skins.secretaryTouch: Hmm? Is there anything I can do for you, Commander?
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Sometimes... I have to endure things I don't like, huh...

skins.shipDescription: Greetings, Commander. I hope I can ask for your continued guidance. ... Hm? Oh dear... I'm Leander, don't you recognise me?
skins.acquisition: Greetings, Commander. I hope I can ask for your continued guidance. ... Hm? Oh dear... I'm Leander, don't you recognise me?
skins.details: Mhm, Commander, it's fine to ask things of me every once in a while.
skins.secretaryIdle2: Though I miss the place where I used to live, the presence of the four seasons here makes it feel like home.
skins.secretaryIdle3: Compared to me, my sisters have much more colourful personalities... *Sigh*...
skins.secretaryTouch: Commander?! Have I made some sort of mistake?!
